folder: Central Park West & 77th Street (West), Manhattan, NY
text:
Central Park West, west side, south from West 81st to West 77th Streets, showing the American Museum of Natural History. The center building (with columns) is the Theodore Roosevelt Memorial erected by the State of New York in memory of the former Governor of the state and President of the United States who was a great naturalist and leader in the conservation movement.

1936.

W.P.A. Photo.
Federal Writers Project.
